    121558,"The Thing from Planet X", 15032,"Space explorers fall under the mental sway of a sentient plant that they collect. After destroying the ship to save Earth they say the crash was accidental since they wouldn’t be believed.",NULL,"Story is pages 10-14 of comic (pages of story numbered 1 to 5).",19);
